name: FitnessCoach
0:
”Alexa, open Fitness Coach”
”Give me a motivational quote”
”Give me instructions for barbell curl”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fitness coach
des:
Fitness Coach will give you step-by-step instructions for any exercise and will motivate you to stay consistent in your fitness journey. 

To get started, you can try saying "Alexa, open Fitness Coach" and make Fitness Coach a part of your fitness routine.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
